Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.47,0:23:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵蚀到至今的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与过去的关联
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.31,0:23:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在于未来的是新的分歧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.82,0:23:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集“苍穹之战神”第13话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.49,0:23:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵蚀 - 异界体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗？
